---
title: Cauliflower Burrito Bowl with Corn Salsa, Avocado & Lemon Yoghurt
description: Try this twist on a burrito bowl, with spiced roasted cauliflower plus classic Mexican sides topping a generous serve of our fragrant garlic rice. It's the ideal recipe to try something new and taste just how versatile veggies can be!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5c19e6ede3f3392e775dded3-25f52058.jpg
